WHERE [m].[UserName] = @__FixEmail_0 AND CASE
    WHEN [m].[PassWord] = @__EncodePasswordMD5_1 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END & [m].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)"
